name: 里德·香农

last_movies.title: 英雄联盟：双城之战 第二季

introduction: Reed Shannon has appeared in many film, television, and theatre productions across the world. You may have seen him Netflix's 4-Time Emmy Winning Animated Series "Arcane" or Amazon Prime's hit YA Series "The Wilds", to name just a few. Reed's ability to sing and act have been recognized by the likes of Berry Gordy early in his career and have led him to an Emmy winning cast with Arcane. Reed grew up in North Carolina then moved to Los Angeles at 15 and began auditioning and studying in the skill of acting. He studied with legendary acting coach Howard Fine in 2019. He also studied for many years at The Groundlings School & Theatre. Reed now lives in Los Angeles, CA!
